    <h1>Passage Indexing</h1>
    <p class="description">A Google ranking system that evaluates <strong>individual sections within a page</strong> independently, letting buried but highly relevant passages rank for specific queries — without the entire page needing to be about that topic.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
